Package com.nickslibrary.datastructures.hashing

Class HashTable<K,V>

java.lang.Object
com.nickslibrary.datastructures.hashing.HashTable<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - the type of keys in this hash table
V - the type of values in this hash table
public class HashTable<K,V> extends Object
A hash table implementation that supports both open addressing and separate chaining collision resolution methods.

      public HashTable(int capacity, HashTable.CollisionResolution resolutionStrategy)

      Parameters:
      capacity - the initial capacity of the table
      resolutionStrategy - the collision resolution strategy (OPEN_ADDRESSING or SEPARATE_CHAINING)

    • HashTable

      Constructs a new hash table with the specified collision resolution strategy and probing strategy.
      Parameters:
      capacity - the initial capacity of the table
      resolutionStrategy - the collision resolution strategy (OPEN_ADDRESSING or SEPARATE_CHAINING)
      probingStrategy - the probing strategy (only applicable for OPEN_ADDRESSING)
